title: Colt Cabana, professional wrestler

description:
Episode 231 - Professional wrestling and independent music? Is there a correlation or connection? I set out with the incredible personality/wrestler Colt Cabana to prove just that. We discuss his life as a wrestler in and out of the “big leagues”, entertaining and tour life. He’s an incredible guy with some great stories. Please enjoy and discover the amazing world of indie wrestling. Get 3 free meals on me! Try out the amazing meal delivery service, Sun Basket.
